<BaseLayout title="About" description="The story behind Watch Stories — why we believe every timepiece has a narrative worth sharing.">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="subtitle">Our Story</div>
    <h1>Why Watch Stories?</h1>
    <p>A watch is never just a watch. It's the first gift you gave yourself. The heirloom your grandfather passed down. The marker of a milestone. We believe every watch has a story — and we're here to help you find yours.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0; color: #555; line-height: 2;">
    <p>Our curated collection brings together timepieces from the world's most respected brands — Seiko, Citizen, Casio, Orient, and more. Not because they're the most expensive, but because they have the most to say.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Whether you're a collector, a first-time buyer, or someone looking for a meaningful gift, we believe the right watch finds you.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent);">— The Watch Stories Team</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
